Capital Markets

Company Overview of Birch Run Capital Advisors, LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Birch Run Capital Advisors, LP doing business as Birch Run Capital is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. It provides its services to high net worth individuals, trusts, corporations or other business entities. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It also launches and manages private funds. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It employs long/short strategy to make its investments. The firm primarily invests in value stocks of companies. It was formerly known as Birch Run Capital, LLC. Birch Run Capital Advisors, LP was founded in May 2006, and is based in New York, New York.


